Author: İbrahim Oğuz Asan [aut, cre, ctb]
Maintainer: İbrahim Oğuz Asan <210527007@stu.istinye.edu.tr>
Description: This is my first R package project for the SWE005 - Multivariate Statistical Analysis with R course. 
    It provides tools for analyzing air quality data and calculating health impacts. 
    The package includes functions for calculating Air Quality Index (AQI), 
    assessing health impacts, and creating visualizations.
